plot: As her ghouls rush to unseal Asura, Medusa stands in the way of Dr. Stein and his students. Elsewhere, Maka decides to settle it once and for all with Crona.
title: Sôru îtâ" Kaishi, chika koubousen. Toppaseyo, Medyûsa no bekutoru aroo?
